room_title: Escape room "The Lost Relic" by The Great Escape of La Crosse in La Crosse
room_description: Your dear friend James works as the local Museum Curator. During his travels searching for hidden treasures, James has made many discoveries and just as many enemies. 5 days ago, he disappeared, but not before getting word to you about his latest discovery. He is leaving what you must assume is a priceless relic, to youâ€¦. if you can find it. Within the walls of his office is hidden all you will need, but can you find it before your time runs out?
